.DT
adjust_alignment
$MUDNAME$ creator help
adjust_alignment

Name
.SI 5
adjust_alignment - Adjusts a living objects alignment.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int adjust_alignment( int number )
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Adjust_alignment() reduces the shift in alignment given by
the (modulus of) the current alignment before using adjusting.
Thus, it will usually not change the alignment to the exact number
given.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_al, set_al, adjust_al, align_string
.EP
